<%- include('partials/head') %>

<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles-pages.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/header.css">

<style>
    .ma
    .legal-body { max-width:760px; margin:0 auto; }
    .legal-body h3 { font-family:var(--pages-font-display); margin:36px 0 12px; color:var(--darkBlue-to-teal12); font-size:1.1rem; }
    .legal-body p { color:var(--pages-text2); margin-bottom:14px; font-size:0.93rem; line-height:1.8; }
    .legal-body ul { margin:0 0 16px 20px; color:var(--pages-text2); font-size:0.93rem; line-height:1.9; }
    .last-updated { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; background:var(--pages-bg3); border:1px solid var(--pages-border); border-radius:50px; padding:5px 14px; font-size:0.8rem; color:var(--pages-text3); margin-bottom:32px; }
    .toc { background:var(--pages-card-bg); border:1px solid var(--pages-border); border-radius:var(--pages-radius-lg); padding:24px; margin-bottom:40px; }
    .toc h4 { font-family:var(--pages-font-display); margin-bottom:14px; }
    .toc ol { margin-left:18px; }
    .toc li { margin-bottom:6px; font-size:0.88rem; }
    .toc a { color:var(--text3); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/header') %>

<div class="page-wrapper">
  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a><span>/</span><span>Privacy Policy</span></div>
      <h1>Privacy <span class="text-gold">Policy</span></h1>
    </div>
  </div>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="legal-body">
        <div class="last-updated">📅 Last Updated: January 1, 2026</div>
        <div class="toc">
          <h4>Table of Contents</h4>
          <ol>
            <li><a href="#information">Information We Collect</a></li>
            <li><a href="#use">How We Use Information</a></li>
            <li><a href="#sharing">Information Sharing</a></li>
            <li><a href="#cookies">Cookies</a></li>
            <li><a href="#rights">Your Rights</a></li>
            <li><a href="#security">Data Security</a></li>
            <li><a href="#contact-us">Contact</a></li>
          </ol>
        </div>

        <p>ZEN TRUST CAPITAL ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you visit our website.</p>

        <h3 id="information">1. Information We Collect</h3>
        <p>We collect information you voluntarily provide when registering, submitting forms, or contacting us, including:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Name, email address, and phone number</li>
          <li>Country and city of residence</li>
          <li>Information about your trading experience</li>
          <li>Communications you send to us</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We also automatically collect technical data such as IP address, browser type, pages visited, and time spent on pages through cookies and analytics tools.</p>

        <h3 id="use">2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
        <p>We use the collected information to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Provide and improve our services and content</li>
          <li>Send you relevant market updates and education materials (with your consent)</li>
          <li>Process IB partnership applications</li>
          <li>Respond to your inquiries and support requests</li>
          <li>Analyze website usage to improve user experience</li>
          <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 id="sharing">3. Information Sharing</h3>
        <p>We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share information with:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Broker partners when you request to open an account (with your explicit consent)</li>
          <li>Analytics providers (Google Analytics) in anonymized form</li>
          <li>Legal authorities when required by law</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We are transparent about our affiliate relationships with brokers. When you click "Open Account" and register with a broker, that broker may also process your data under their own privacy policy.</p>

        <h3 id="cookies">4. Cookies</h3>
        <p>We use cookies to enhance your browsing experience. See our <a href="/cookies" style="color:var(--pages-gold);">Cookie Policy</a> for full details. You can control cookies through your browser settings or our cookie consent tool.</p>

        <h3 id="rights">5. Your Rights</h3>
        <p>Under applicable data protection laws, you have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
          <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
          <li>Object to processing of your data</li>
          <li>Data portability</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
        </ul>
        <p>To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <span id="email-id" class="emailRedirect text-gold""><%- include('partials/email') %></span></p>

        <h3 id="security">6. Data Security</h3>
        <p>We implement industry-standard security measures including SSL/TLS encryption, secure servers, and regular security audits. However, no internet transmission is 100% secure.</p>

        <h3 id="contact-us">7. Contact Us</h3>
        <p>For privacy-related questions, contact our Data Protection Officer at <span id="email-id" class="emailRedirect text-gold""><%- include('partials/email') %></span> or through our <a href="/contact" style="color:var(--pages-gold);">contact form</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>

  <script src="/js/theme.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/emailWhatsAppRedirect.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
